 ] .


###  https://w3id.org/DOLCE/OWL/DOLCEbasic#PhysicalQuality
:PhysicalQuality rdf:type owl:Class ;
                 rdfs:subClassOf :Quality ,
                                 _:genid299 ,
                                 _:genid301 ;
